item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

(pi base)Okay so I am working on making a barbarian agility course for my server.

I make the int in player.java barbObsticle

and I make mew case in Actionhandler.java

case 2294://logbalancebarb if (c.absX == 2550 && c.absY == 3546 && c.gnomeObsticle == 1) { c.obsticle(762, 1, 0, -7, 5000, 500, "You passed the obsticle succesfully."); c.barbObsticle = 1; } else if (c.absX == 2550 && c.absY == 2550) { c.obsticle(762, 1, 0, -7, 5000, 500, "You passed the obsticle succesfully."); }

My problem is this, why does it still teleport me to the gnome course? How would I make it to just go to the end of that course.
